<th style="">Signature</th>
<td class="" style=""><a href="/wiki/File:Jeremy_Bentham_signature.jpg" class="image" title="Jeremy Bentham signature.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/3/35/Jeremy_Bentham_signature.jpg/128px-Jeremy_Bentham_signature.jpg" width="128" height="46" border="0" /></a></td>
